'tut.quit':'Quit tutorial','tut.skip_step':'Skip this step','tut.next':'Next','tut.done':'Done','tut.do_it':'Your turn','tut.missing':'This element isn’t available right now — tap Next to continue the tour.',
'tut.welcome_t':'Welcome!','tut.welcome_d':'This short tour teaches the app by doing — you perform each action yourself. It runs in a sandbox: nothing you do here is saved, your real collection stays untouched. Quit anytime with Esc.',
'tut.open_card_t':'Open a card','tut.open_card_d':'Everything starts with a card. Each card exists in several variants (base, foil, dual…) that you track separately. Tap a card to open its detail and manage them.',
'tut.mark_owned_t':'Add to your collection','tut.mark_owned_d':'The core gesture. Tap + on a variant to mark it owned: your progress, stats and badges all update from what you own. Try it now.',
'tut.mark_double_t':'Count your doubles','tut.mark_double_d':'Tap + again to reach 2 copies. Every copy beyond the first is a double — the app tracks them so you know exactly what you can trade.',
'tut.close_modal_t':'Close the card','tut.close_modal_d':'Close the detail however you like: the ✕, a tap outside, or a swipe down on mobile.',
'tut.favorite_t':'Favourites','tut.favorite_d':'No need to open a card for quick changes: the chips on each card toggle a status in one tap. Tap the heart to mark this card a favourite — you can then pin favourites first in the grid.',
'tut.wishlist_t':'Wishlist','tut.wishlist_d':'The star adds a card to your wishlist: the cards you are hunting for. It feeds the “missing cards” and trade lists in the collector tools.',
'tut.sidebar_open_t':'Filters','tut.sidebar_open_d':'A big collection is tamed with filters. Open the panel to slice the grid by status, category, type, rarity or year.',
'tut.filter_apply_t':'Apply a filter','tut.filter_apply_d':'Tap a rarity to show only those cards. Filters combine: stack rarity + category + status to zero in on exactly what you need.',
'tut.filter_reset_t':'Reset','tut.filter_reset_d':'One tap brings the full grid back — no need to undo each filter one by one.',
'tut.sidebar_close_t':'Close the panel','tut.sidebar_close_d':'Close it however you prefer: the ✕, a tap on the dimmed background, or a swipe left.',
'tut.search_t':'Search','tut.search_d':'The fastest way to a specific card: type a driver, a team or a card name — the grid narrows as you type.',
'tut.go_badges_t':'Badges','tut.go_badges_d':'Badges are the trophies of your collection: some unlock automatically as it grows, others you validate yourself. Open the Badges tab.',
'tut.badge_manual_t':'Validate a badge','tut.badge_manual_d':'Manual badges reward real-life feats (attending a race, completing a trade…). Tap one to validate it yourself — you decide.',
'tut.badge_remove_t':'Remove a badge','tut.badge_remove_d':'Made a mistake? Remove mode lets you un-validate any badge, even one that unlocked automatically.',
'tut.go_stats_t':'Stats','tut.go_stats_d':'Stats turn your collection into a dashboard: completion, trends, records. Open the Stats tab.',
'tut.stats_progress_t':'Progress','tut.stats_progress_d':'Your overall completion at a glance, and how it grows over time — this is what every card you mark owned feeds.',
'tut.stats_highlights_t':'Highlights','tut.stats_highlights_d':'The pride of your collection: your rarest owned card and your biggest stack of doubles.',
'tut.stats_donut_t':'By rarity','tut.stats_donut_d':'How your collection spreads across rarities — a quick way to spot where the gaps are.',
'tut.go_settings_t':'Settings','tut.go_settings_d':'Last stop: Settings, where you make the app yours and keep your collection safe. Open the tab.',
'tut.set_theme_t':'Theme','tut.set_theme_d':'Light or dark, whichever is easier on your eyes. The choice is remembered on this device.',
'tut.set_font_t':'Fonts','tut.set_font_d':'Five font themes restyle the whole app in one tap. (Driver numbers keep their racing identity whatever you pick.)',
'tut.set_backup_t':'Backup','tut.set_backup_d':'Your collection lives only on this device. Generate a code or a QR here to carry it to another device — nothing is ever uploaded.',
'tut.set_data_t':'Import / Export','tut.set_data_d':'For a full safety net, export your whole collection as a file — and re-import it anytime, right here.',
'tut.set_tools_t':'Collector tools','tut.set_tools_d':'Ready-to-share lists: the cards you are missing, your doubles to trade, and a combined trade list for your next swap.',
'tut.replay_t':'All set!','tut.replay_d':'You know everything! Replay this tour anytime from this button. Remember: nothing you did during the tour was saved — your collection is exactly as you left it.',
'install.title':'💻 Install the app','install.label':'Use it as a real app','install.sub':'Full screen, its own icon, fully offline — on your dock, desktop or home screen.','install.btn':'📲 Install','install.installed':'Already installed — you are using the app right now.','install.banner':'Install F1 UNO Élite as an app?','install.later':'Not now','install.ins_ios':'In Safari: tap Share (the square with an arrow), then “Add to Home Screen”.','install.ins_mac':'In Safari: File menu → “Add to Dock…”.','install.ins_chromium':'Click the install icon at the right end of the address bar, or menu ⋮ → “Install app”.','install.ins_android':'In Chrome: menu ⋮ → “Add to home screen” / “Install app”.','install.ins_generic':'Open this site in Chrome, Edge or Safari and use its “Install app” / “Add to Home Screen” option.','install.ins_arc':'Arc doesn’t support installing web apps (no install icon in its address bar). Open this site in Chrome, Edge or Safari to install it.',
